description:
Added drum track. Should be nearly perfect.

I adjusted the rhythm of the guitar/bass parts since the timing was adjusted to fit the drums. The song starts with a pickup note, but the guitar tabs were written without that, so I had to move everything forward 1 eighth-note, and had to adjust rhythms in the chorus and bridge sections to fit. They may need to be checked again. I modified my MP3 in Audacity to bring out the guitar more to try and get the rhythms correct, but I'm not 100% certain.

I condensed the guitar parts from the unnecessary 4 tracks into 2 tracks, and named all tracks.

No Vocal track yet.
title: 1000hp
